# New app playbook

Source data: sibling repo `docs/APP_STORE_LISTING_*.md`, `GOOGLE_PLAY_LISTING_*.md`, `AppConfig` (bundle ID, legal URLs, support email).

## Pre-launch (under construction)

1. `lib/appPublishState.ts` → `{APP}_PUBLISHED = false`
2. Landing: icon, hero, “Coming Soon”, links to privacy/terms
3. `sitemap.ts`: privacy + terms only
4. **Skip** `siteCatalog.ts`, `AppsGrid`, `AppsCarousel` until published

## Go live

1. Set `{APP}_PUBLISHED = true`
2. Full product page + store badges
3. Add to `siteCatalog.ts`, home grid/carousel, `llms.txt`
4. Verify App Store / Play URLs (HTTP 200, correct package ID)
5. Update `appStructuredData.ts`

## Copy icon

```bash
cp /path/to/AppRepo/assets/app_icon_512.png public/images/{slug}-icon.png
```

Support email default: `zuki.apps.dev@gmail.com`. Legal URLs: `https://zukiapps.com/{slug}/privacy` and `/terms`.
